<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chalet Suizo | Galería Interactiva</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --cafe-oscuro: #3C2A21;
            --cafe-medio: #5E454B;
            --cafe-claro: #D5CEA3;
            --crema: #E5E5CB;
            --blanco: #FFFFFF;
            --sombra-texto: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; }
        body { background-color: var(--blanco); color: var(--cafe-oscuro); line-height: 1.6; }

        /* --- Barra de Navegación --- */
        nav {
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 10%; background: var(--cafe-oscuro); color: var(--crema);
            position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1000;
        }
        nav .logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: 2px; }

        .hero {
            height: 60vh;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)), 
                        url("file:///C:/Users/maryc/Downloads/20221105_132834.jpg.jpeg"); 
            background-size: cover; background-position: center;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
            text-align: center; color: var(--blanco); padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .hero h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 3.5rem; text-shadow: 2px 2px 15px var(--sombra-texto); }

        .featured-container {
            display: flex; padding: 60px 10%; gap: 50px; align-items: flex-start; flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .gallery-wrapper { flex: 1; min-width: 350px; }
        
        .slider-container {
            position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 15px 15px 0px var(--cafe-claro); aspect-ratio: 4/3; cursor: zoom-in;
        }

        .slider {
            display: flex; width: 500%; 
            height: 100%; animation: slide 20s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        .slider img { width: 20%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

        @keyframes slide {
            0%, 15% { transform: translateX(0); }
            20%, 35% { transform: translateX(-20%); }
            40%, 55% { transform: translateX(-40%); }
            60%, 75% { transform: translateX(-60%); }
            80%, 95% { transform: translateX(-80%); }
            100% { transform: translateX(0); }
        }

        /* --- Cuadro de texto debajo del carrusel --- */
        .info-extra-box {
            margin-top: 35px;
            padding: 25px;
            background-color: var(--crema);
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 1px dashed var(--cafe-medio);
        }

        .modal {
            display: none; position: fixed; z-index: 2000; top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
            justify-content: center; align-items: center;
        }
        .modal-content { max-width: 90%; max-height: 80%; border-radius: 10px; border: 3px solid var(--crema); }
        .close-modal { position: absolute; top: 30px; right: 50px; color: white; font-size: 40px; cursor: pointer; }

        .featured-details {
            flex: 1.2; min-width: 350px; background: #FDFDFD; padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px; border-left: 8px solid var(--cafe-oscuro);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .featured-details h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--cafe-claro); padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .detail-section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .detail-list { list-style: none; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .btn-reserva {
            display: block; width: 100%; padding: 15px; background: var(--cafe-oscuro);
            color: var(--crema); text-align: center; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px; transition: 0.3s;
        }

        /* Estilo para la lista de tarifas */
        .tarifas-list li {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 5px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
            .featured-container { padding: 30px 5%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav><div class="logo">Chalet Suizo</div></nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <h1>Refugio privado de inspiración Alpina</h1>
        <p>"Donde el tiempo se detiene y la naturaleza comienza"</p>
    </header>

    <section class="featured-container">
        <div class="gallery-wrapper">
            <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--cafe-medio);"> Haz clic en las imágenes para ampliar</p>
            <div class="slider-container" onclick="openZoom()">
                <div class="slider" id="mainSlider">
                    <img src="file:///C:/Users/maryc/Downloads/20260202_164455.jpg.jpeg" alt="Fachada 1" class="zoomable">
                    <img src="file:///C:/Users/maryc/Downloads/20260202_164433.jpg.jpeg" alt="Interior" class="zoomable">
                    <img src="file:///C:/Users/maryc/Downloads/20221105_131831.jpg.jpeg" alt="Mezzanine" class="zoomable">
                    <img src="file:///C:/Users/maryc/Downloads/20260202_164546.jpg.jpeg" alt="Terraza" class="zoomable">
                    <img src="file:///C:/Users/maryc/Downloads/20260202_164949.jpg.jpeg" alt="Fogatero" class="zoomable">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-extra-box">
                <h3>Tu estancia ideal</h3>
                <p>Ubicado en La Trinidad zona emblemática por sus minas de ópalo y a una distancia de 15 min del centro de Tequisquiapan. 
Nuestro Chale fusiona el diseño alpino con la arquitectura mexicana moderna. Un refugio diseñado para el relax absoluto, ideal para parejas, familias o grupos selectos que buscan reconectar.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="featured-details">
            <h2>Detalles del Chalet</h2> 
            
            <div class="detail-section">
            
            </div>

            <div class="detail-section">
                <h3>🏠 Planta Baja</h3>
                <ul class="detail-list">
                    <li>🍳 Cocineta equipada, estufa 4 quemadores, frigobar.</li>
                    <li>🚿 Baño completo (ecotecnología-solar 🔆).</li>
                    <li>🛋️ Salita de estar con sofá cama y terraza.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-section">
                <h3>🪜 Mezzanine</h3>
